{"id":232884023,"title":"相機都掉價這麼快的嗎!?","content":"因為課程的需要，去年10月中買了Fujifilm的X-T30+18-55kit\n當時相機王現金價是31400(尾數忘了，總之差不多三萬一)刷卡價好像是32x00\n當時尋遍各大FB二手社團，都找不到30000以下的價格(而且二手貨都被秒殺)\n結果才過了三個月，就掉了快2000元!(趁現在截圖下來，看過幾個月會不會再掉)\n相機的行情都是這樣的嗎?因為富士也還沒出新款，為什麼價格就掉得這麼多阿?\n我買的時候他也已經出一陣子了阿，不是說剛出就馬上買，我的分期付款才繳到第二期耶嗚嗚...\n雖然我買是買了，也享受到了，沒什麼好怨的(只是心裡不太舒服QQ)\n因為我是新手，所以我只是好奇相機的行情都這樣，還是說和品牌有關呢?\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/H4rBGPr.jpg","excerpt":"因為課程的需要，去年10月中買了Fujifilm的X-T30+18-55kit，當時相機王現金價是31400（尾數忘了，總之差不多三萬一）刷卡價好像是32x00，當時尋遍各大FB二手社團，都找不到30","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d0cd5819-4627-4b5f-8a8e-050976e0fba1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-13T11:22:32.217Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T11:22:32.217Z","commentCount":14,"likeCount":8,"tags":[],"topics":["微單"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"攝影","forumAlias":"photography","school":"國立臺北教育大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/H4rBGPr.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"a8aa2b05-74d7-423e-bdb4-29e688b531cf","url":"https://i.imgur.com/H4rBGPrl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/H4rBGPrl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/H4rBGPrl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-13T11:22:32.217Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T11:22:32.217Z"},{"id":"a8aa2b05-74d7-423e-bdb4-29e688b531cf","url":"http://i.imgur.com/H4rBGPr.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/H4rBGPr","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/H4rBGPrl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-13T11:22:32.217Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T11:22:32.217Z"}],"postAvatar":""}